.site-block.site-block--large
  .container-fluid
    .row
      .col-12.col-sm-10.offset-sm-1
        .row
          .col-12.col-lg-5.d-flex.flex-wrap.align-items-start.align-content-start
            header
              h2 data-sal="slide-up" data-sal-delay="600" data-sal-duration="1000" Join the collective.
            p data-sal="slide-up" data-sal-delay="700" data-sal-duration="1000" We’re an invite only collective so we grow slowly and carefully.
